2011-12-05  Didier Verna  <didier@xemacs.org>

	* slime.el ([xemacs]): Don't require 'un-define in XEmacs 21.5 and
	later. Mule-UCS is not needed anymore because of internal Unicode
	support (and conflicts with it).

