	(backtrace, frame-locals-for-emacs): Use it.

2007-11-29  Tobias C. Rittweiler  <tcr@freebits.de>

	* swank.lisp (valid-function-name-p): Fixed wrt. setf functions.

2007-11-29  Helmut Eller  <heller@common-lisp.net>

