	* swank.lisp (*sldb-printer-bindings*): Add *print-right-margin*.
	(debug-in-emacs): Bind *sldb-printer-bindings* here ...
	(backtrace, debugger-info-for-emacs, frame-locals-for-emacs):
	... and remove redundant bindings here.

