2005-08-07  Matthias Koeppe  <mkoeppe@mail.math.uni-magdeburg.de>

	Fix for the presentations menu.  Reported by Aleksandar Bakic.

	* present.lisp (lookup-presented-object): Handle ids that are
	conses.
