	* slime.el (save-some-lisp-buffers): New Function.
	(slime-repl-only-save-lisp-buffers): New customizable variable.
	(slime-repl-compile-and-load): Use save-some-lisp-buffers.
	(slime-oos): Use save-some-lisp-buffers.

